Task submited in the thread will not be counted.Funds Escrowed address: https://arbiscan.io/tx/0xb307c44f78fc4f39ba85e50f184e8d27fd89f0f6812bac6ce1e3a036b19e2509Update for Telegram and Discord participants:1. Those who have joined the Discord and telegram campaigns need to join the discussion in the server. If we haven't found any messages from you every week in the project server and telegram group, you won't get any stake. 2. After the start of a week we will stop allowing new participants for that week, and their entries will start counting from next week.3. If you are rejected in the Telegram campaign, fill out the form again by following the rules we will start counting your stake from the next week. It is not allowed to remove your avatar or personal text. If caught we will reject your approval for that week.11/12/2023: Edit: Change of rule 1:1. The team is not happy about the spamming happening in the project telegram group and discord server. So there is a small change of rules: Join discussions in other active crypto-related telegram groups and on the Discord server. Copy that message link and submit it through google doc. For week 1 those who are approved in the spreadsheet will get their stake. From week 2, new rules will be applied.19/12/2023: Edit: Due to the spamming in the main projects telegram and discord group the team got bad impression from the project investors and decided to discontinue the telegram and discord campaign from week 2. All the participants who got stake in week 1 will get their token but the allocation will be 1/4 and 3/4 of the allocation for the telegram and discord campaign will evenly distributed to twitter, article and video campaign. All the participants can now remove their avatar and personal text from their profile.
